an%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Ghamidi&amp;rft.aufirst=Javed&amp;rft.au=Ghamidi%2C+Javed&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BAl-Mawrid%7CDar+ul-Ishraq%5D%5D&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Jihad"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
